  <brief_title>Pre-treatment Exercises Versus Post-treatment Exercises for Dysphagia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Determining the Efficacy of Pre-treatment Swallowing Therapy as a Means to Improve Dysphagia Quality of Life When Compared to Post-Treatment Therapy.</official_title>
