  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this project is to determine if pre-treatment swallowing exercises can improve
      post-treatment swallowing function in patients undergoing radiation with or without
      chemotherapy for advanced squamous cell carcinoma of the head and neck.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
